---
import VideoLink from "../components/VideoLink";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import {
  BiLogosReact,
  BiLogosNodejs,
  BiLogosAngular,
  BiLogosRedux,
  BiLogosPhp,
  BiLogosJquery,
  BiLogosHtml5,
} from "solid-icons/bi";
---

<MainLayout title="Mauricio Allende - Front-end Engineer">
  <article class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
    <section class="prose">
      <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="mb-0 mt-4">Globant</h2>
        <a
          target="__blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://www.globant.com/"
        >
          globant.com
        </a>
        <a
          class="mt-0"
          target="__blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://latamairlines.com"
        >
          LATAM XP
        </a>
        <strong class="mt-2 text-gray-5">2019 - 2020</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mt-12">
        <VideoLink
          class="max-w-32 h-20 w-full"
          src="/videos/codepen/latam.mp4"
          url="https://codepen.io/mallendeo/pen/ExVPLjB"
        />
      </div>

      <p class="mt-12">
        In 2020, I worked at Globant with the LATAM Ancillaries Team to redesign
        and create the user interface for seat selection and baggage services.
      </p>
      <p>
        We used <strong>Next.JS</strong> and <strong>Node</strong> on Google Cloud
        Platform (GCP). We worked using a monorepo (Lerna) where we shared UI components
        with other teams.
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-10">
        <BiLogosReact
          title="React / Next.JS"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-cyan"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosNodejs
          title="Node.JS"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-emerald"
          size={24}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10" />

    <section class="prose">
      <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="mb-0 mt-4">AcidLabs</h2>
        <a
          target="__blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://acidlabs.com/"
        >
          acidlabs.com
        </a>
        <strong class="mt-2 text-gray-5">2019</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mt-4">
        <VideoLink
          class="max-w-48 h-42 w-full"
          src="/videos/codepen/abcdin.mp4"
          url="https://codepen.io/mallendeo/pen/EMBjvg"
        />
      </div>

      <p class="mt-0">
        I worked on the Abcdin e-commerce platform, where I fixed bugs, improved
        performance, and added new features.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also improved their React Native app performance on the map
        navigation, and the server response time for the in-store Kiosks by more
        than 80%.
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-10">
        <BiLogosReact
          title="React / React Native"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-cyan"
          size={24}
        />
        <BiLogosRedux
          title="Redux"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-indigo"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosNodejs
          title="Node.JS"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-emerald"
          size={24}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10" />

    <section class="prose">
      <div class="flex justify-center mix-blend-multiply">
        <VideoLink
          class="max-w-32 h-32 w-full"
          src="/videos/codepen/reign.mp4"
          url="https://codepen.io/mallendeo/pen/NyJqRv"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="mb-0 mt-4">Reign Design</h2>
        <span>Now ApplyDigital</span>
        <a
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="__blank"
          href="https://www.applydigital.com/reign/en/"
        >
          applydigital.com
        </a>
        <strong class="mt-4 text-gray-5">2018</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mt-16">
        <VideoLink
          class="max-w-48 w-full"
          src="/videos/codepen/falabella.mp4"
          url="https://codepen.io/mallendeo/pen/EQoage"
        />
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8">
        I developed the user interface for an insurance web app for Seguros
        Falabella.
      </p>
      <p>
        In addition, I created a proof of concept for an interactive payment
        user interface for Copec, utilizing Falabella Pay.
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-10">
        <BiLogosAngular
          title="Angular 4+"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-red"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosNodejs
          title="Node.JS"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-emerald"
          size={24}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10" />

    <section class="prose">
      <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="mb-0 mt-4">Pleno</h2>
        <span>Santillana</span>
        <a
          target="__blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://www.pleno.digital/"
        >
          pleno.digital
        </a>
        <strong class="mt-4 text-gray-5">2017</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="my-16"></div>

      <p>
        I created a multi-platform app that allows students in rural areas to
        take offline tests that can later be uploaded to the Santillana platform
        Pleno for evaluation.
      </p>

      <p>
        The app includes a real-time admin dashboard that makes it easy for the
        professor to pause or finish the test for any or all students. A video
        of the app flow is available at <a
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="__blank"
          href="https://youtu.be/nP8HFSCk7KI"
        >
          youtu.be/nP8HFSCk7KI
        </a>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-10">
        <BiLogosAngular
          title="Angular 4"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-red"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosNodejs
          title="Node.JS"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-emerald"
          size={24}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10" />

    <section class="prose">
      <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="mb-0 mt-4">Frankenstudio</h2>
        <span>Freelance</span>
        <a
          target="__blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://www.facebook.com/FRKS2"
        >
          frankenstudio
        </a>
        <strong class="mt-4 text-gray-5">2014 - 2015</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="my-16"></div>

      <p>
        I created
        <a
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="__blank"
          href="https://www.facebook.com/FRKS2/videos/obus-open-building-system/673147469452507/"
        >
          OBUS (Open Building System)</a
        >, a platform that displays useful information on various screens around
        the <em>Casa Central</em> campus of the <em
          >Pontificia Universidad Cat√≥lica de Chile.</em
        >
      </p>

      <p>
        This system includes an admin panel where publishers can upload media
        and create posts relevant to the campus and university. These apps are
        interactive, touch-friendly, and can be easily deployed on a new screen
        and configured via the admin panel.
      </p>

      <p>
        In 2015, I developed a video recording app with a green screen effect
        from scratch for
        <em>Minera Los Pelambres</em>. With this app, you can send a video
        postcard to yourself or anyone via email. The app runs on NW.js (Node
        Webkit) and was coded without a framework.
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-10">
        <BiLogosPhp
          title="CakePHP"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-red"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosNodejs
          title="Node.JS / Node Webkit"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-emerald"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosHtml5
          title="HTML5"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-orange"
          size={24}
        />

        <BiLogosJquery
          title="jQuery"
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-emerald"
          size={24}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="prose bg-gray-1 p-4 rounded-lg mt-8">
      P.S. All the animations on this page were made with code. You can click
      any of the animations, and it will take you to their respective <strong
        >CodePen</strong
      > page.
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
